{"tid":123063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【公審】文青小店漫活X拖糧　網友FB專頁義助　僱主發聲明不道歉","createTime":"2017-02-16T14:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T05:43:42.000Z","uid":85252,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0e4ec0a29b117085d388ca94b545e2edc2818d","tid":123063,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"寫低係想大家搵工小心Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<del>　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　</del><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前係太子嘅文青小店「漫X堂 」做兼職<br />\n但一月初發覺老細遲遲未出糧<br />\n就同老細反映話未出糧（過左7日犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n咁之後過多左個星期終於出到糧，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就無啦啦再無被排落更表<br />\n一月低大年初一，仲俾人靜靜雞剔出職員whatspp group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原本都諗住算<br />\n穩穩陣陣等佢出埋一月份糧就算（2月7日）<br />\n點知漫X堂拖到到2月11號都無動靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走去問下D 其他同事<br />\n先知原來曾經有兼職同事欠薪一個月先出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係玩蓄意拖糧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後決定做D野<br />\nemail 去公司提出三個要求<br />\n1. 立即出糧<br />\n2. 書面解釋事件<br />\n3. 保證其他兼職員工可以準時出糧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男友同時去佢facebook page炸佢問點解唔出糧<br />\n朋友如我見狀，留言幫拖<br />\nfb admin呢頭話跟進，轉頭就連個post都delete埋<br />\n擾攘一輪，page 都閂埋&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWq4746.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWq4746.png&h=4e74330a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到岩岩個星期一，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總算追番欠薪<br />\n但漫活X又無道歉，又無解釋，更唔承諾日後準時出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家仲見佢 Facebook Page 開番<br />\n出聲明話對網友留言保留法律追究權利&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34x378L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34x378L.jpg&h=b7f3a430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都怕再去留言會俾佢告，係到打，真係希望大家小心搵part time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dff49364784df4fd4a43f15f0fccb1194e6b4a6","tid":123063,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0cdaab6459485a8c2e4a1a29d8959d711f2ed0","tid":123063,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b7c03e29f44fd76617ed284bc0fa7e61570964","tid":123063,"uid":5834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"點解要怕？"},{"pid":"43bba248b8345126dd586ea10b19810d9b86f7c4","tid":123063,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要怕？</blockquote><br />\n真係告落黎，無錢無律師都唔知點算?<br />\n<br />\n我都係普通打工仔，俾老細知有官司，隨時炒埋我"},{"pid":"a5605e0980e0cbfaf47e3f95e00513f3e7a69d01","tid":123063,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解要怕？</blockquote><br />\n真係告落黎，無錢無律師都唔知點算?<br />\n<br />\n我都係普通打工仔，俾老細知有官司，隨時炒埋我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去勞記會幫你告啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁怕事抵俾人拖人工"},{"pid":"7d35aab213b5aa16191af74449b5de030ae801aa","tid":123063,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a397ad2a9f4c0b9755fc878fde88bc8e99d875b","tid":123063,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:32:09.000Z","msg":"拖糧果個告人？你估呢度大6咩，只要件事佢有做 就算佢想告9你 上到庭你估個官屌唔屌9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57502f01b28a9ecf668dd7743c5e8d5ff2593948","tid":123063,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"老細係邊個"},{"pid":"959a9af198f1276cdb4601e6357dc00caec59d02","tid":123063,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解要怕？</blockquote><br />\n真係告落黎，無錢無律師都唔知點算?<br />\n<br />\n我都係普通打工仔，俾老細知有官司，隨時炒埋我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去勞記會幫你告啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁怕事抵俾人拖人工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n亞視單野前居可鑑，去勞記追&hellip;&hellip;之前都查過，執法不力，每年仲有好多單欠薪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n// 2016年工聯會指出勞資審裁處於1999年至2014年有合共57369宗有關欠薪的個案，然而由1999年直至2015年6月，只有13人因欠薪被罰處入獄，可見欠薪問題相當普遍，而刑責卻未見有阻嚇作用。[5]2016年的亞洲電視欠薪事件中，亞視的執行董事葉家寶亦在被票控102張欠薪傳票下，獲判罰15萬港元，屬香港近年一大欠薪事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25B5%2584&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f86a08b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84</a>"},{"pid":"bce5a03e0165ece1f1112af3bacbef21391316c5","tid":123063,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老細係邊個</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔駛怕喇，佢都block左我lu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/slowlifehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fslowlifehk%2F&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=624d919e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/slowlifehk/</a>"},{"pid":"c66f1699d6c173277c6080cb8c3e48d90576e822","tid":123063,"uid":73408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"份聲明 X活堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a995748907024f434ba11a03b6062083121b4297","tid":123063,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c865055d2e3dce8e0c8f6366f71429d625bd778","tid":123063,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d8b4a665cacb02d31c4f491717f4507ade99a8","