lip;<br />\n<br />\n灰到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小市民如我又驚佢告我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想硬起來佢又已經block左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真，唔知點解你要驚，依家佢犯法，驚都係佢地驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議你將個post send去薯片或者胡官facebook，佢地依家拉緊票，一定會幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb7860d49d223362e6c578c38d826a7dbcbe26e","tid":123063,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留言唔夠五分鐘就被消失"},{"pid":"3834a70a7256d071b972d4be2eb23fbf5d88a466","tid":123063,"uid":25916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"拖人糧仲要炒人真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e7286791bb7c3a1184658f2ffa00fdb7324000","tid":123063,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾d火黎<br />\n<br />\nbtw阿火哥單野點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個時個post話上到庭阿火哥俾個官問到口啞啞，當時樓主好似話結果要保密，就無理lu"},{"pid":"0415e6da0ab353c3c697b1221b0e0f2302107ae3","tid":123063,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留言唔夠五分鐘就被消失</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都唔想追究，真心係想大家小心搵工<br />\n講真，個facebook admin都可能係受薪做<br />\n糧都唔係佢拖（或者佢都俾人拖緊OT糧）"},{"pid":"b543b2b3e1fddff36ee2a0d20f4aa9794b56711a","tid":123063,"uid":79009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\"